Add baseline renal function class

Source: R/nif_class.R
add_bl_renal.Rd

Add baseline renal function class

Usage

add_bl_renal(obj, method = egfr_cg)

Arguments

obj

A NIF object.

method

The function to calculate eGFR (CrCL) from serum creatinine. Currently either: egfr_mdrd, egfr_cg or egfr_raynaud

Value

A NIF object.

Examples

as.data.frame(add_bl_renal(examplinib_poc_nif))
